# ambiguity — Python implementation

## Location
`src/ambiguity/` — Federation-facing Python package

## Key files
- `containers.py` — verb taxonomy + keyword map + acronym registry
- `parser.py` — regex token extraction
- `scoring.py` — ambiguity score (0-10) formula
- `advisory.py` — priority-ordered advisory rules
- `bridges.py` — UDL envelope (optional Federation import)

## Testing
```bash
pytest tests/
ambiguity analyze "test" --json
```

## Conventions
- No LLM calls — all regex + dict + arithmetic
- Federation bridge fails silently if C:\Federation unavailable
- Match ts/src/ patterns exactly (same modules, same logic)
